OL,5,EAM I MISSING OUT?            Wvs|||a} 
OL,6,E                                   W*%
OL,7, Dear Nick,                             
OL,8, BNone of my mates have dated a guy as  
OL,9,B long as I have. I've been seeing my   
OL,10,B boyfriend for 18 months, and I love   
OL,11, Bhim to bits, but something tells me   
OL,12, BI'm missing out.                      
OL,14, BI just get this feeling that my mates 
OL,15, Bare out having a better time, and I'm 
OL,16,B doing steady things. So now I'm stuck 
OL,17,BB- should I dump the man I love, or    
OL,18, Bmiss out on the fun of being single?  
OL,19, GLouise fan                            
OL,20, ``````````````````````````````````1/2``
