OL,5,EAM I MISSING OUT?            Wvs|||a} 
OL,6,E                                   W*%
OL,7, Nick replies,                          
OL,8, BTheBgrass always seems greener on the 
OL,9, Bother side. If you haven't got a      
OL,10, Bboyfriend you want one and vice versa.
OL,11, BBut boys aren't for life. If things   
OL,12, Baren't working, try being single.     
OL,14, BDuring your teens it's madness to get 
OL,15, Binvolved because you don't know what's
OL,16,B round the corner. Don't get too cosy  
OL,17, Btoo soon. Maybe the best thing to do  
OL,18, Bis talk to him, see how he feels.     
OL,19, BIs a trial split possible?            
